artre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-7-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"The minimalist room features a Policronica aesthetic with wooden furniture, white walls, and a high ceiling. A small table, chairs, couch, and decorative plants enhance the serene space where neutral tones dominate.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-7-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-7-800x1066.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-7-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-7-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568012\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568012\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-8-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist cafe interior featuring wooden tables and chairs, a brown cushioned bench, and a table lamp is beautifully complemented by Policronica framed artwork on the beige wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-8-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-8-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-8-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-8-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/