025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-10-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePolicronica’s Lisbon-based workshop operates as an incubator for end-to-end production, eliminating the fragmentation typically seen in construction and furniture manufacturing. Designers, architects, carpenters, and industrial specialists collaborate under one roof, streamlining processes that would traditionally be divided across multiple suppliers. This integrated workflow reduces inefficiencies and fosters innovation in sustainable manufacturing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568015\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568015\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-10a-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist living room featuring Policronica wooden furniture, a white sofa with two tan cushions, a unique chair, lamp, and framed art. Exposed brick and beams add rustic charm to the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-10a-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-10a-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-10a-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-10a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568016\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568016\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-11-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"In a minimalist living room, the wooden ceiling and beige walls frame a Policronica-inspired low wooden sofa. Two round chairs and a large coffee table complement modern wall lights, while a textured rug adds subtle depth to the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-11-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-11-800x601.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-11-768x577.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568017\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568017\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"The minimalist living room features a wooden coffee table, cream sofa, and mustard pillows. Wall art and a textured rug enhance the space. Neutral tones and natural light highlight the modern décor, creating a policronica ambiance that\u0026#39;s both elegant and timeless.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12-800x1066.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568018\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568018\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12m-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"The minimalist living room features wooden furniture, a beige sofa, and abstract artwork. A textured rug complements the exposed brick wall, creating a striking contrast with the modern decor. The Policronica touch infuses harmony into this refined space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12m-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12m-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12m-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-12m.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOne of the most groundbreaking advancements introduced in this project is Policronica’s development of solar vacuum wood dryers. These innovative drying chambers significantly accelerate the natural curing process of eucalyptus wood, reducing the timeframe from 18 months to just six days while ensuring stability and durability. Additionally, by maximizing the use of each tree trunk and eliminating unnecessary transportation between processing facilities, the project maintains an exceptionally low carbon footprint.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568019\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568019\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-13-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist room with a wooden table, textured wall, and arched window overlooking greenery. A Policronica bench is placed against the wall beneath a modern vertical light fixture, creating a sophisticated yet serene atmosphere.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-13-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-13-800x1066.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-13-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568020\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568020\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-14-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A Policronica wooden door with a brass handle stands elegantly next to a sheer curtain.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-14-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-14-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-14-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-14-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568021\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568021\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-15-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist living room with a wooden staircase, large windows, and neutral tones. It features a cozy armchair, a round table with decor, and Policronica framed artwork that adds an artistic touch.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-15-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-15-800x601.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-15-768x577.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThroughout the hotel rooms, Policronica tapped raw materials, such as wood, plant fibers, brass, and neutral fabrics, to form a monochromatic, organic interior that is anything but bland. Each room evokes the feeling of being at home, if one lived in a stylish Parisian apartment, with warmth and coziness right in the middle of an urban environment.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568022\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568022\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-16-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"This minimalist room features wooden decor and a Policronica touch. A round side table holds a silver tea set, paired with a cream chair and mustard cushion. Framed artwork adorns the wall, while beige curtains softly filter the light through the window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-16-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-16-800x601.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-16-768x577.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568023\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568023\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-17-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room featuring wooden furniture and two large windows with beige curtains exudes a policronica charm. A circular table, decorative lamps, and a fruit bowl add to the ambiance. On the left, stairs with wooden slats elegantly complete this stylish space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-17-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-17-800x601.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-17-768x577.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568024\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568024\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-18-810x810.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist living room with wooden furniture, a round table, a geometric chair, a tall lamp, and framed art exudes effortless elegance. Two large windows with beige curtains reveal an outdoor view of trees, creating a serene policronica scene.\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-18-810x810.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-18-800x800.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-18-100x100.jpg 100w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-18-768x768.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-18-300x300.jpg 300w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568025\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568025\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-19-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"The minimalist bedroom features a double bed with white bedding and brown pillows, complemented by two wooden lamps on side tables. A wooden chair sits in front, while Policronica reflects in the framed artwork above the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-19-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-19-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-19-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-19-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568026\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568026\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-20-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy bedroom features a white armchair, small wooden table, and stool near two windows. Light curtains frame the windows; a framed Policronica painting rests on a cabinet beside the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-20-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-20-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-20-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-20-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568027\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568027\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-21-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"The minimalist bedroom features a white bedspread with two beige and orange pillows, accentuated by the Policronica aesthetic. Wall-mounted lamps illuminate symmetrical wooden nightstands, while a brown accent wall hosts a framed piece of art above the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-21-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-21-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-21-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568028\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568028\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-24-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"The street view showcases a building facade with Policronica\u0026#39;s signature wooden-framed arched windows. Inside, the decor is minimal, featuring artwork on the wall and a plant. The exterior pavement stretches invitingly in the foreground.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-24-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-24-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-24-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-24-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Elysee-Montmartre-Hotel-Paris-Policronica-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on the Elysée Montmartre Hotel, visit \u003ca href=\"https://emhotel.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eemhotel.fr\u003c/a\u003e, and for more on Policronica, head to \u003ca href=\"https://www.policronica.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003epolicronica.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography courtesy of Policronica.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
